---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="Our affiliate disclosure policy regarding Amazon and Walmart affiliate links."
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-14">

    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-forest mb-3">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-green prose-lg max-w-none">

      <h2>What this means</h2>
      <p>
        A Green Family (agreenfamily.com) participates in affiliate marketing programs, including the
        <strong>Amazon Associates Program</strong> and the <strong>Walmart Affiliate Program</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        This means that when you click a link on this site to a product on Amazon or Walmart and make a purchase,
        we may earn a small commission — at <strong>no additional cost to you</strong>. The price you pay is the same whether you use our link or navigate directly to the retailer.
      </p>

      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with the U.S. Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines on endorsements and testimonials
        (16 CFR Part 255), we disclose our affiliate relationships clearly. This disclosure appears:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>On this dedicated disclosure page</li>
        <li>In the footer of every page on this site</li>
        <li>At the top of each article that contains affiliate links</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our product recommendation policy</h2>
      <p>
        We only link to products that we genuinely believe are useful and relevant to the article's topic.
        Affiliate commissions do not influence which products we recommend or what we write about.
        We do not accept payment from brands to feature their products.
      </p>

      <h2>Amazon Associates</h2>
      <p>
        A Green Family is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising
        program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>

      <h2>Walmart Affiliate Program</h2>
      <p>
        A Green Family participates in the Walmart Affiliate Program via the Impact affiliate network.
        When you purchase through our Walmart links, we may earn a commission.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or this disclosure, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@agreenfamily.com">hello@agreenfamily.com</a>.
      </p>

    </div>

  </article>
</Layout>
